1
00:00:20,600 --> 00:00:22,440
Why are you still alive?

2
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:24,800
You should go to hell.

3
00:00:28,680 --> 00:00:30,440
Give me back my life.

4
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:33,880
Go to hell.

5
00:00:35,880 --> 00:00:37,040
So tragic.

6
00:00:38,800 --> 00:00:40,280
Give me back my life.

7
00:00:40,280 --> 00:00:41,640
Go to hell.

8
00:00:42,720 --> 00:00:43,640
Song Ping.

9
00:00:43,800 --> 00:00:45,520
Why can you still be alive?

10
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:49,280
Song Ping.

11
00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:50,410
Give me back my life.

12
00:00:55,400 --> 00:00:57,200
Song Ping.

13
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:59,600
Give me back my life.

14
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:05,800
Song Ping.

15
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:09,039
Give me back my life.

16
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:11,080
Song Ping.

17
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:13,680
I died such a tragic death.

18
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:34,720
No one can help you now.

19
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:39,440
Didn't you perish

20
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:41,370
with those Japanese underground?

21
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,320
With him?

22
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:47,600
He wanted to trade his life for mine.

23
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,720
So are they really all dead?

24
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:52,850
You have already seen them,

25
00:01:53,240 --> 00:01:55,400
and even wrote a report about it.

26
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:57,680
That means

27
00:01:59,080 --> 00:02:01,080
they are really dead.

28
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:03,800
And now,

29
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:07,600
I will avenge those wronged souls.

30
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,600
Come to claim your life.

31
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:24,840
My lord.

32
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:25,680
My lord.

33
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:26,800
I beg you.

34
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:27,600
Please save me.

35
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:28,060
Save me.

36
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:29,720
I will manage Taohua Town well for you.

37
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:30,560
I will.

38
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:52,280
You saw them die with your own eyes

39
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:54,800
and reported it in an official document.

40
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,260
Naturally, they are dead.

41
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:02,000
I understand.

42
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,930
So you wanted to use me as a mouthpiece.

43
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:07,060
Tell outsiders

44
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:10,980
that there are no living people left in Taohua Town.

45
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:16,460
Chief Song, you are indeed smart.

46
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:17,760
This way,

47
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:20,340
anyone who wants to enter Taohua Town

48
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,520
and take this away

49
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:24,000
will have to think twice.

50
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:33,240
So you guys are in this together.

51
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,970
More than just knowing each other,

52
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:40,130
our relationship is not ordinary.

53
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:41,320
Right, Dad?

54
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:45,880
Good thing I arrived in time.

55
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,240
Wang Shiqi.

56
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:55,600
Otherwise,

57
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,680
if something happens to

58
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,610
this pretty daughter-in-law,

59
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,800
that brat

60
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:04,880
would never let me hear the end of it.

61
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,480
I don't want to be a wandering ghost.

62
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:17,360
I don't want to be a wandering ghost.

63
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:17,959
Song Ping.

64
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:18,800
I don't want to be a wandering ghost.

65
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,200
You've done so much evil.

66
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,160
Today,

67
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,730
I will use your blood

68
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:25,900
to pay tribute to the innocent souls you killed.

69
00:04:28,520 --> 00:04:29,400
Good, good, good.

70
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:30,120
Good riddance.

71
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:30,980
Good riddance.

72
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,280
I forgot to sharpen the knife.

73
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:35,040
And you won't even become a ghost.

74
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:35,480
Good.

75
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,159
Good.

76
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:37,060
Brother Shiqi.

77
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:46,520
Good thing I gave you this back then.

78
00:04:47,200 --> 00:04:49,400
Thank you for bringing your troops, Madam,

79
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:50,800
wiping out those devils,

80
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,340
and saving the whole town.

81
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,840
Protecting the borders and the people

82
00:04:53,840 --> 00:04:55,159
is a soldier's duty.

83
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:58,400
It's also thanks to Miss Su risking her life

84
00:04:58,400 --> 00:04:59,800
to send the message in time,

85
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,400
that a disaster was avoided.

86
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,930
The person you really should thank...

87
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:04,530
It's her.

88
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:10,720
It's a pity.

89
00:05:12,080 --> 00:05:13,410
To the rest of the world,

90
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:16,480
you are all dead now.

91
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:23,660
It's better to be dead.

92
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,640
We've all discussed it.

93
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:26,880
From now on,

94
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:28,640
we will all become ghosts

95
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:31,400
to protect the precious cultural relics

96
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:32,600
buried underground.

97
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:33,520
Okay.

98
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:35,600
The mayor didn't report the news

99
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,000
that everyone was alive.

100
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:39,760
Taohua Town was forgotten during the war.

101
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:41,880
And only by turning this place into a ghost town

102
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:43,280
can we deter tomb raiders

103
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:46,280
and temporarily protect the national treasures.

104
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:50,920
You brat.

105
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,450
You did a good job this time.

106
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,400
I will continue to wander around

107
00:05:53,400 --> 00:05:54,840
the world

108
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,170
and uphold justice.

109
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:57,500
What do you say?

110
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:58,930
Want to come with me?

111
00:06:02,760 --> 00:06:04,040
I certainly want to.

112
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:05,040
But

113
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:08,040
I haven't got a wife yet.

114
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:08,760
Think about it.

115
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:09,620
If I follow you,

116
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:12,040
I'm afraid I'll really become a eunuch.

117
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,200
You blockhead.

118
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:15,440
I was anxious to have a grandson.

119
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:17,170
How could you believe my bluff?

120
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,840
I knew it all along.

121
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:26,960
I was just

122
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:28,840
trying to make you happy.

123
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:30,640
After all, I'm your son.

124
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:33,600
But, Dad,

125
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:35,520
this time,

126
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:37,680
I've made up my mind.

127
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,680
I want to stay here

128
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:41,840
to continue protecting underground cultural relics.

129
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:43,170
I can't let those relics

130
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:45,240
fall into the hands of foreigners.

131
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,500
I believe that one day,

132
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:49,159
we can completely drive them

133
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:50,520
all out.

134
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:51,280
Good.

135
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:52,440
Ambitious.

136
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:53,920
Wang Shiqi!

137
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:57,440
Brother Wang!

138
00:06:57,440 --> 00:06:58,320
You executioner!

139
00:06:58,320 --> 00:07:00,650
Does your promise to marry me still count?

140
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:03,040
You said you'd compensate me with your body.

141
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,280
I still haven't got it.

142
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:04,640
Me...

143
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:05,370
Give it to me!

144
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,040
Brother Wang!

145
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:07,680
You!

146
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:08,640
You deal with it.

147
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:09,640
You can't either!

148
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:10,960
Dad!

149
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:11,520
You!

150
00:07:11,520 --> 00:07:12,450
You can't leave!

151
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:12,960
I...

152
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:14,080
I've made up my mind.

153
00:07:14,080 --> 00:07:15,080
I'll follow you.

154
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:16,560
I want to wander around the world with you.

155
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,240
I can't

156
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,570
handle this situation!

157
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:20,440
I can't be careless

158
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:23,700
about choosing my daughter-in-law.

159
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:26,770
Do you see this copper coin?

160
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:30,600
Whoever gets this coin

161
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:33,280
will be the daughter-in-law of the Wang family.

162
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:34,010
Give it to me!

163
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:34,640
I want it.

164
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:54,770
This is mine.

165
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:57,600
I'm really going to become a eunuch.

166
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:09,000
Dad!

167
00:08:12,400 --> 00:08:13,120
Dad!

168
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:14,920
Okay.

169
00:08:15,280 --> 00:08:16,560
Tell Dad today,

170
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,520
what you four little rascals

171
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:19,840
have been up to again.

172
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,160
Today, two more tomb raiders

173
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,420
were scared away by us.

174
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:24,410
Awesome.

175
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:25,400
Then

176
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:26,700
tell us the story of

177
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:29,160
how you slayed ghosts back then.

178
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:33,080
Tell us.

179
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:34,159
Tell us, Dad.

180
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:35,600
Alright.

181
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:36,280
Stop.

182
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:37,490
Stand still.

183
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,049
Stand still.

184
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:41,679
Then Dad

185
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,559
will tell you again

186
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:45,760
the stories of those ghosts.

187
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:48,280
Are these stories true?

188
00:08:51,040 --> 00:08:52,240
Whether they are true

189
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,320
or false,

190
00:08:54,640 --> 00:08:55,440
remember,

191
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:59,120
it's all to protect our national treasures

192
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:01,170
from being coveted by bad guys.

193
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:02,770
Why does good always

194
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,180
triumph over evil?

195
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,800
To deter those bad guys,

196
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:07,920
just like

197
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,720
the stories Dad told.

198
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:17,700
Come on.

199
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:18,600
Children,

200
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:19,420
come to Mom.

201
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:21,240
Come to Mommy.

202
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:21,880
Come here.

203
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:23,040
Auntie.

204
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:23,440
Mom.

205
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:25,640
Auntie bought you some delicious food.

206
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:26,800
Come.

207
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:28,560
Come here.

208
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,040
I want a hug too.

209
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:33,760
Mom.

210
00:09:33,760 --> 00:09:36,420
Mommy will take you to eat something good, okay?

211
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:40,560
Good.

212
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:43,360
Maybe,

213
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,040
it's all an illusion.

214
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:51,160
Who knows?

215
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,800
Wanrong and I have four children.

216
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:56,080
Yinlian and Jiaojiao became my siblings.

217
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,560
The happiness makes me a bit dazed.
